Long-term effectiveness of aripiprazole once-monthly for schizophrenia is 
maintained in the QUALIFY extension study.

Naber D(1), Baker RA(2), Eramo A(3), Forray C(4), Hansen K(5), Sapin C(6), 
Peters-Strickland T(7), Nylander AG(8), Hertel P(9), Nitschky Schmidt S(10), 
